<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Y2K-MAIN-0103-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EXPERTS LOOK FOR LINGERING Y2K BUGS AS BUSINESSES OPEN MONDAY
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ As factories, doctors' offices, banks and other
businesses resume full operations Monday, computer experts will be
